{"url": "https://aplus.com/a/this-is-us-lonnie-chavis-responds-to-bullies-on-instagram?no_monetization=true", "text": "He addresses the bullies by telling them to \"fix their hearts,\" and points out that bullying hurts people.\n\n\"Fix your heart, though. For real,\" he continues. \"I'm happy that I can handle this ... I'm not tripping.\"\n\nHe points out that there are kids who cannot handle the trolling. Lonnie says to them, \"If y'all kids are watching this, don't trip. Be who you want to be. Do what you want to do. Do you. Be you. Believe in yourself.\"\n\nHis written message ends, \"You are beautiful, you are awesome, and you matter!\"\n\nCommenters of all ages are applauding the young man for rising above the bullies, and promoting a positive message.", "images": ["https://cdn5.aplus.com/assets/mobile/nav/tumblr-e9ac0073ef34f889ea80041cffc785d83944016126296ba842c86155c6781529.png", "https://images5.aplus.com/380x220/uc-up/e4861126-bb93-4e91-9d07-bf1d22e1cb5b/e4861126-bb93-4e91-9d07-bf1d22e1cb5b.crop_1010x530_0,133.resize_1200x630.format_jpeg.inline_yes.jpg", "https://cdn5.aplus.com/assets/close-notification-modal-0ac5418f9064fb885a8f69c72958d3862781f27b95940093540b97a9dcf8f1bb.png", "https://cdn5.aplus.com/assets/aplus-logo-bd818654faabbd94d892b2eacfd9f6d9bf1c3a326371b4ad6e0b37adb1ba994d.png", "https://images5.aplus.com/380x220/uc-up/b892d88f-a7c5-435a-b76f-ca957ced22ac/b892d88f-a7c5-435a-b76f-ca957ced22ac.crop_5760x3024_0,375.resize_1200x630.format_jpeg.inline_yes.jpg", "https://cdn5.aplus.com/assets/mobile/nav/instgram-6a4708f5029ca5861326221602ccefd7451868afd2b3279bcb8bbbbbc60b1d9d.png", "https://cdn5.aplus.com/assets/aplus_logo_white-6141173fb2f35a62f94cfff70b3b3c022691defb4e6aa50bae3ad6e1460fdb9d.png", "https://cdn5.aplus.com/assets/mobile/nav/facebook-e5643e5ea8df6f63dcb341e8ec703ebae6e92e796b7ab4c2e7b7e9be337d29e9.png", "https://cdn5.aplus.com/assets/mobile/nav/youtube-ff92d450ad69e9329c56ea47f91fdd20d45b35ae5206a0a2f1b4412809dc2154.png", "https://imag